{"id":140622,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/03/简讯：杭州副市长贪腐两亿多受审/","date":"2011-03-19T14:00:25Z","modified":"2011-03-19T14:00:25Z","title":"简讯：杭州副市长贪腐两亿多受审","content":"<div>\n<p>被控受贿、贪污和滥用职权的原浙江杭州市副市长许迈永在宁波接受了审判。</p>\n<p>许迈永被控在1995年至2009年期间受贿超过1.6亿元人民币，及贪污5300多万元。</p>\n<p>他还被控徇私舞弊让他人非法得到7100万元土地出让金。</p>\n<p>根据以往的类似案例判断，许迈永有可能被判处死缓甚至死刑。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/FZ0GyworLyeQAwh7IqKAjTByF7Y/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/FZ0GyworLyeQAwh7IqKAjTByF7Y/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/FZ0GyworLyeQAwh7IqKAjTByF7Y/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/FZ0GyworLyeQAwh7IqKAjTByF7Y/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/i7RNZB_m_K4\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><b>要翻墙？(发邮件到Gmail):CDTcaonimaATgmail.com</b></p>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}